name: Fragmented Self-Potraits I
description:
During the blackout of Covid-19 I decided to start taking pictures of myself and my surroundings, because, well, it was all I was able to reach back then. As hard to believe as it is, Argentina back in January 2021 was one of the countries with the hardest restrictions all over the world. That inspired me to show my new tiny world as I lived it.

Fragmented Self-Potraits I by Arianna Tafa
Buenos Aires, Argentina
January 2021
